import React, {Component} from 'react'
import {Layout, Menu, Skeleton, Card, Avatar, Row, Col } from 'antd';
import { EditOutlined, EllipsisOutlined, DeleteOutlined } from '@ant-design/icons';

import './favourites.less'
/*
头部组件
 */
const { SubMenu } = Menu;
const { Content, Sider } = Layout;
const { Meta } = Card 

export default class Favourites extends Component{
    state = {
        theme:'light',
        loading: false
    }

    render(){
        const {loading} = this.state
        return(
            <Layout className="favourites">
                <Sider className="favourites-sider" theme={this.state.theme}>
                    <Menu className="favourites-sider-menu" mode="inline"
                    defaultSelectedKeys={['1']} defaultOpenKeys={['sub1']}
                    >
                        <Menu.Item key="0">option1</Menu.Item>
                        <SubMenu key="sub1" title="subnav 1">
                        <Menu.Item key="1">option1</Menu.Item>
                        <Menu.Item key="2">option2</Menu.Item>
                        <Menu.Item key="3">option3</Menu.Item>
                        <Menu.Item key="4">option4</Menu.Item>
                        </SubMenu>
                        <SubMenu key="sub2" title="subnav 2">
                        <Menu.Item key="5">option1</Menu.Item>
                        <Menu.Item key="6">option2</Menu.Item>
                        <Menu.Item key="7">option3</Menu.Item>
                        <Menu.Item key="8">option4</Menu.Item>
                        </SubMenu>
                    </Menu>
                </Sider>
                <Layout>
                <Content className="favourites-content">
                    <Row>
                        <Col span={8}>
                            <Card style={{ width: 300}}
                            actions={[
                                <EditOutlined key="edit" />,
                                <DeleteOutlined key="delete" />,
                                <EllipsisOutlined key="ellipsis" />,
                            ]}
                            >
                                <Skeleton loading={loading} avatar active>
                                    <Meta
                                    avatar={<Avatar src="https://zos.alipayobjects.com/rmsportal/ODTLcjxAfvqbxHnVXCYX.png" />}
                                    title="Card title"
                                    description="This is the description"
                                    />
                                </Skeleton>
                            </Card>
                        </Col>
                    </Row>
                    <Row>
                        <Col span={8}>
                            <Card style={{ width: 300}}
                            actions={[
                                <EditOutlined key="edit" />,
                                <DeleteOutlined key="delete" />,
                                <EllipsisOutlined key="ellipsis" />,
                            ]}
                            >
                                <Skeleton loading={loading} avatar active>
                                    <Meta
                                    avatar={<Avatar src="https://zos.alipayobjects.com/rmsportal/ODTLcjxAfvqbxHnVXCYX.png" />}
                                    title="Card title"
                                    description="This is the description"
                                    />
                                </Skeleton>
                            </Card>
                        </Col>
                    </Row>
                    <Row>
                        <Col span={8}>
                            <Card style={{ width: 300}}
                            actions={[
                                <EditOutlined key="edit" />,
                                <DeleteOutlined key="delete" />,
                                <EllipsisOutlined key="ellipsis" />,
                            ]}
                            >
                                <Skeleton loading={loading} avatar active>
                                    <Meta
                                    avatar={<Avatar src="https://zos.alipayobjects.com/rmsportal/ODTLcjxAfvqbxHnVXCYX.png" />}
                                    title="Card title"
                                    description="This is the description"
                                    />
                                </Skeleton>
                            </Card>
                        </Col>
                    </Row>
                    <Row>
                        <Col span={8}>
                            <Card style={{ width: 300}}
                            actions={[
                                <EditOutlined key="edit" />,
                                <DeleteOutlined key="delete" />,
                                <EllipsisOutlined key="ellipsis" />,
                            ]}
                            >
                                <Skeleton loading={loading} avatar active>
                                    <Meta
                                    avatar={<Avatar src="https://zos.alipayobjects.com/rmsportal/ODTLcjxAfvqbxHnVXCYX.png" />}
                                    title="Card title"
                                    description="This is the description"
                                    />
                                </Skeleton>
                            </Card>
                        </Col>
                    </Row>
                </Content>
                </Layout>
            </Layout>
        )
    }
}
